        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/08bc702ee1369e640299d46107b85adf?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
                "account_id": 423440,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 802831,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/802831/ji%c5%99%c3%ad-vyp%c4%9bd%c5%99%c3%adk",
                "reputation": 1334,
                "display_name": "Jiř&#237; Vypědř&#237;k",
                "accept_rate": 17
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1332934170,
            "creation_date": 1332934170,
            "body": "<p>Servlet 3.0 specification supported by JBoss 7.1 allows specification of session cookie path in web.xml. Just put this fragment to all of your wars whose context you want to be shared:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;session-config&gt;\n    &lt;cookie-config&gt;\n        &lt;path&gt;/&lt;/path&gt;\n    &lt;/cookie-config&gt;\n&lt;/session-config&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 9906562,
            "question_id": 8604889
        }
